           <p style=3D"margin: 0; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 30px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0;">Greetings from Los Angeles,=
 and welcome back to In the Room. In tonight=E2=80=99s email, more news and=
 notes on the turbulence at the <i>Washington Post</i>, where a week=E2=80=
=99s worth of restructuring, strategically placed leaks, and finger-pointin=
g seems to be driving <b>Jeff Bezos</b>=E2=80=99s beleaguered paper toward =
yet <i>another</i> nadir. Is a late-Friday plea from <b>Will Lewis </b>enou=
gh to <i>fix it</i>?<br/><br/><i>But first, a couple CNN scoops</i>=E2=80=
=A6<br/><br/>=F0=9F=93=BA <i>A primetime change</i>: CNN C.E.O. <b>Mark Tho=
mpson </b>has elevated <b>Anderson Cooper</b>=E2=80=99s longtime executive =
producer <b>Charlie Moore</b> to vice president of news, overseeing the 7 p=
=2Em. to midnight hours. Moore is one o=
f the most highly respected E.P.s at t=
he company, and his move to primetime may portend further changes to the ne=
ws network=E2=80=99s struggling nighttime lineup. To her credit,
<b>Kaitlan Collins</b> has been playing to her strengths recently with some=
 <i>very</i> well-conducted interviews (<b>Bill Barr</b>, etcetera) that ac=
tually make for <i>good television</i>, but the ratings indicate the broade=
r primetime strategy is long overdue for an overhaul. <br/><br/>=F0=9F=92=
=BB <i>An A.P. deal</i>: CNN has struck a deal with the Associated Press to=
 use their copy for digital stories, the first time it has done so since cu=
tting ties with the wire service in 2010. The deal would appear to portend =
further staff cuts, and that=E2=80=99s certainly how some CNN insiders are =
reading it. A spokesperson tells me it=E2=80=99s simply intended to free up=
 reporters to spend more time on original, longform, and investigative repo=
rting. =E2=80=9CThis allows our writers to spend more time on enterprise re=
porting and less time on quick writes,=E2=80=9D the spokesperson said. =E2=
=80=9CThe goal is to enhance our editorial reach while allowing us to focus=
 on key editorial priorities.=E2=80=9D<br/></p>
